features: 🚗 WIDE COMPATIBILITY - Input: 12V-24V; Output:5V/2A. 13ft Dash Cam Hard Wire Kit supports Mini USB and Type-C port types with all car mini dashcam such as dashcam, mirror cam, GPS navigator, accepts cam, accepts voltage from any type of vehicle runs on 12-24V.

📸 COMPLETE DASH CAM HARDWIRE KIT - Are you frustrated by not having the right tools for your own installations? CESOO has created the most complete set of mini USB hardwire kit. You will get 1 x Mini USB Hardwire Kit,1x Type-C Adapters, 1x power test pencil,1 x installing crowbar, 4 x fuse tap cable, can meet the installation needs of 99% of the car models on the market.

🕙 24 HOURS SURVEILLANCE - The vehicle hard-wire kit, which is connected to the power from the fuse box or the car battery, It can be continuously powered 24/7 . It works uninterruptedly even if the car is turned off. Protect your car every time.

🔌 UNDERVOLTAGE PROTECTION - For our 2024 updated version, We've upgraded the Auto Power Off Protection feature so that the Hardwire Kit Mini USB will automatically cut off power when the car's voltage falls below 11.6V. This prevents the car from failing to start due to low battery voltage.

🌞 HIGH SECURE STANDARDS - CESOO mini USB hardwire kit with built-in precise switching power supply module can transform 12V(24V) to 5V. The wire is made of high quality copper as the conductive material, which can greatly increase the service life of the wire and avoid the risk of fire due to the aging of the wire.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 8, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Imo worth it
reviews.reviewText: The install wasn’t too difficult for a diy er like myself. I really appreciate the extra parts that come with this kit like the different types of fuse taps, fuses for the fuse taps, and the other hardware included. If I were to get all this separately, I probably would’ve spend a little more than what I had spent on this kit… which is why I think this kit was worth it and it works well with my Type S 4K dash cam.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 14, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great all in one DIY hardwire kit for your dash cam
reviews.reviewText: I love that this kit comes with just about everything needed for a DIY installation of a dash cam. Technically it could be everything needed, I just happen to have a plastic rivet tool I also used, but the pry bar included would have worked.It comes with multiple fuse taps, zip ties, pry bar, simple voltage presence probe, etc. It also has built in protection to keep your device from contributing to battery drain.Altogether great kit to grab if you want to go hard wire and want everything to DIY.
